name: tompkins-county-building-outlines-dwg-2005
notes: CAD-friendly version (DWG format) of building polygons representing houses, businesses, mobile homes, barns, silos and other buildings that could be determined from aerial photography, using photogrammetric mapping technologies and HouseDiff feature extraction process.
